{"tid":810694,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【樓爆2018】太古城租金暴跌$8000！！！","createTime":"2018-09-08T07:36:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-08T16:18:43.000Z","uid":43146,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d3b128ad3a870cfded714fb39a0269cdc4b964f5","tid":810694,"uid":43146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T07:36:15.000Z","msg":"中原地產表示，太古城9月錄得11宗租賃成交，平均實用呎租42元，旗下分行近日促成租賃成交單位為太古城碧藤閣高層A室，實用面積1,114平方呎，建築面積1237平方呎，3房套間隔及工人房，坐享全海景。業主4月放租，經內部裝修後叫價52,000元，最終減8000元以44000元租出，折合平均實用呎租39元。<br />\n<br />\n該行太古城區副區域營業董事趙鴻運透露，租客屬於公司客。業主於2007年7月以950萬元買入單位，持貨11年，租金回報5.6%。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a15f15c8faabae08e8132d8f5b1fbe481fa4fea8","tid":810694,"uid":21134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T07:46:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c09ce26ee2a378ecc955ca5ea0cbe490d294450","tid":810694,"uid":119897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T08:02:34.000Z","msg":"租黎自用 唔計"},{"pid":"7cf098fa63b6f8b4b52447acfe7e13b89a166697","tid":810694,"uid":125261,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T08:07:06.000Z","msg":"七八月暑假係租務旺季，九月開左學就淡靜，年年都係咁"},{"pid":"4451e025763cadabee22765d4e73a6a52ad9ecb1","tid":810694,"uid":23385,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T08:09:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/08/160910_2cdb5eacf55ca1e94130c04a9b0a6862.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F08%2F160910_2cdb5eacf55ca1e94130c04a9b0a6862.png&h=bd3b97dc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e60f599f1f8b632991379f90109a125a22aea6ed","tid":810694,"uid":122377,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T08:36:45.000Z","msg":"又話業主加租？"},{"pid":"5be38fd43e0537b1de44fd7f80b4ec97f18d49f8","tid":810694,"uid":43146,"like":